<!DOCTYPE html><html ⚡><head> <% include ../../_partials/amp/_amp-head.ejs %><link rel="canonical" href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/Recording"></head><body class="home"><amp-sidebar id='sidebar' side='right' layout='nodisplay'> <% include ../../_partials/amp/_ampLandingSidebar.ejs %></amp-sidebar><header class="header fixed"> <% include ../../_partials/amp/_amp-header.ejs %></header><div class="wrap"><div class="container main"> <% include ../../_partials/content/_bluenav-general.ejs %><article class="blade wrapper content"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="twelve columns"><h1>Aufnahme Menü</h1></div></div> <!-- ##################################### Schedule ############################################ --><div class="card-container margin"><div class="twocard"><a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/Recording/Schedule/"><div class="image"><amp-img noloading height=400 width=400 layout=responsive src="/images/720p_webUI/QL-Box_WebUI_Recording_Schedule_mouseOver.png"></amp-img></div></a><div class="action"><p>This is the schedule that will be used for planned recordings and the photoseries. Just select the service you want to use and fill out a time window for this function to be active in. Every blue block inside the schedule stands for a 30min window of activity.</p></div></div> <!-- ##################################### Video ############################################ --><div class="twocard"><a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/Recording/Video/"><div class="image"><amp-img noloading height=400 width=400 layout=responsive src="/images/720p_webUI/QL-Box_WebUI_Recording_Video_mouseOver.png"></amp-img></div></a><div class="action"><p>Here you can activate the planned video recording. This function will record a video to the cameras internal SD card inside the time window defined by the Recording Schedule. You can set the resolution and length of each recorded video file.<br><br></p></div></div></div> <!-- ##################################### Photoseries ############################################ --><div class="card-container margin"><div class="twocard"><a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/Recording/Photoseries/"><div class="image"><amp-img noloading height=400 width=400 layout=responsive src="/images/720p_webUI/QL-Box_WebUI_Recording_Photoseries_mouseOver.png"></amp-img></div></a><div class="action"><p>Record snapshots in an adjustable time interval and stitch them together inside a Third-party Software to create a timelapse video. You can also choose to upload the snapshot with a fixed file name. This will always overwrite the last file and allows you to easily embedd a Live Image of your IP camera inside your homepage.</p></div></div><div class="twocard invisible"></div></div></div></section></div></div> <% include ../../_partials/content/_bluenav-general-mobile.ejs %><footer> <% include ../../_partials/amp/_amp-footer.ejs %></footer></body></html>